{%- doc -%}
  Resolves whether out-of-stock variants should be HIDDEN for a given product.

  Single source of truth for the "Hide Out-of-Stock Variants" feature. Combines the global theme
  setting (settings.hide_oos_variants) with the per-product override metafield
  (custom.oos_variant_visibility: "Use global setting" | "Hide Out-of-Stock Variants" |
  "Show Out-of-Stock Variants"). The product override always wins; otherwise the global setting applies.

  Outputs the string "true" or "false" — capture it and compare:
    {%- capture hide_oos -%}{%- render 'oos-visibility', product: product -%}{%- endcapture -%}
    {%- assign hide_oos = hide_oos | strip -%}
    {%- if hide_oos == 'true' -%} assign vlist = product.variants | where: 'available', true {%- endif -%}

  @param {object} product - the product to evaluate
{%- enddoc -%}
{%- liquid
  assign override = product.metafields.custom.oos_variant_visibility.value | default: '' | downcase
  if override contains 'hide'
    echo 'true'
  elsif override contains 'show'
    echo 'false'
  elsif settings.hide_oos_variants
    echo 'true'
  else
    echo 'false'
  endif
-%}
